  ('optometrist-moex-03454', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '某一老花患者，其遠用眼鏡度數為+3.00 DS，其調節量（amplitude of accommodation）為2.00 D，習慣近 閱讀距離為33.3公分，請問此老花患者的近閱讀眼鏡度數為下列何者最適當？', '["+1.00 DS", "+3.00 DS", "+5.00 DS", "+7.00 DS"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b04495330ac2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8ea1edd93f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03455', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '受檢者戴用-3.00 DS的隱形眼鏡，可以看清楚的最近距離是10公分。已知受檢者的最大調節力是8.00 D， 拿掉隱形眼鏡後，可以看清楚的最遠距離是？', '["8公分", "12公分", "20公分", "25公分"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b04495330ac2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8ea1edd93f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
